Julio RODRIGUEZ, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11022. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 14, 1946. Andersen & Resner and Herbert Res-ner, all of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Theron Lamar Caudle, Asst. Atty. Gen., James W. Knapp and Roscoe T. Pile, Attys., Dept. of Justice, both of Washington, D. C., and Frank J. Hennessy, U. S. Atty., of San Francisco, Cal., for appellees.

Before GARRECHT, MATHEWS, and .HEALY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed.
